I'd use:

```├── TransformationFiles
│   ├── MappingMapToCanLocARA_A.xslt
│   └── MappingMapToModelLocARA.xslt
└── ValidationFiles
    ├── CanLocARA_A.xsd
    ├── CanLocARA_B.xsd
    ├── ModelLocARA.xsd
    └── SourceLocARA.xsd```


`SourceLocARA.xsd -> MappingMapToCanLocARA_A.xslt -> CanLocARA_A.xsd`  (CSV OUTPUT)
`CanLocARA_B.xsd -> MappingMapToModelLocARA.xslt -> ModelLocARA.xsd`    (UPX OUTPUT)
Those are the two transforms that we're interested in
and the second one (the one to model loc ARA) should have the `.upx` option
